name: China Southern 777-31BER [B-2099] Landing at Vancouver Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Another video from my YVR trip back in May. Here we have one of China Southern's many 77Ws landing runway 26R arriving from Guangzhou. Never seen China Southern's 77W before, it sure looks good, if not a little dated ;) ATC is included, enjoy!

Thanks for watching!
